37202>>>>>                    // Store the login
37202>>>>>                    If (bUpgrade) Begin
37204>>>>>                        Get CreatePasswordHash (Trim(sPassword)) (&sPassword) to bUpgrade
37205>>>>>                        If (bUpgrade) Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.Password to sPassword
37208>>>>>                    End
